show.title: Mr.Fu Spoils his wife too much

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/e6Lm2b
show.description: Forced into marriage with a man she despises, her life becomes a storm of anger and resistance. But when fate unveils a twisted glimpse of their shared future, the rules of their relationship change forever. A powerful tale of passion, destiny, and the thin line between hate and love.
